reviewText: The soundtrack is wonderful and so is the setting of the movie.  A fun family film. For a low budget independent film this was a great work.
This is a good wholesome film for the entire family to watch together. It should teach some values. The Neville Girl did a good job, too bad it must have been her only film.
THIS IS A GREAT INSPIRATIONAL FAMILY FILM ABOUT A HEARING IMPAIRED BASKETBALL PLAYER.IT'S A MUST SEE!!!
